                     <summary> Oriental semi-cursive scripts</summary>
                     <handNote><persName key="person_7046">Ḥalfon ben Ẓedaḳah</persName> (colophon on <locus>fol. 389v</locus>) copied only <locus>fols. 231-235 and 347-389</locus>. The rest is a compilation of two different MSS. (<locus>fols. 95-224 and fols. 236-346</locus>), which were completed by a later scribe who copied <locus>fols. 2v-94r and 225-230</locus>.</handNote>
